<paragraph blockId="5.[136,1452,158,1120]" box="[189,930,1094,1120]" pageId="5" pageNumber="97">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,328,1094,1120]" pageId="5" pageNumber="97">Etymology:</emphasis>
─The specific epithet describes the pale pink flowers.
</paragraph>
